name: Dylan Dog 3: Storia di Nessuno
overview: White night, freezing snow on the tombstones ... Mr. Nobody dies and is reborn. Xabaras the alchemist, Xabaras the sorcerer, has returned again to play with the life of the dead and with the death of the living. But this time it has unleashed forces it cannot control. Not even he knows that even in the heart of any Nobody, suspended between this world and the next, entire universes are hidden ...
